Name: Park concrete pump in location & setup within designated area
Tag 1: Park concrete pump in location and setup within designated area. Line set-up not to disturb formwork, reinforcement and starter bars. Communication between operator and formwork in place

Name: All pipelines/rubbers, safety chains, locking pins securely fitted
Tag 1: Has all pipelines/rubbers, safety chains, and locking pins been adequately and securely fitted

Name: Placing boom movement coordinated with crane crew
Tag 1: Has the placing boom movement been coordinated with the crane crew (if applicable)

Name: OHS&R and Environmental Measures
Tag 1: OHS&R and Environmental Measures: All safety, PPE requirements in place. MSDS sheets supplied. All documentation is current as per Project OHS&R Plan and EMP Plan. All Site personnel have been inducted. Environment Controls in Place.

Name: Sand & plastic membrane in place where required
Tag 1: Is there sand and plastic membrane in place where required in accordance with Structural specification and AS 3600?

Name: Formwork cleaned sufficiently to take concrete placement
Tag 1: Has the formwork been cleaned sufficiently to take concrete placement? Ensure the formwork and other trades have cleaned areas in accordance with Structural Specification and AS 3600.

Name: All movement joints are placed in accordance
Tag 1: Are all movement joints are placed in accordance Structural Specification

Name: Has the laser been calibrated to the required level
Tag 1: Has the laser been calibrated to the required level

Name: Percentage of the element is ready for GB
Tag 1: What percentage of the element is ready for GB prior of the commencement of the pour

Name: All trades completed works in the designated pour area
Tag 1: Has all trades completed works in the designated pour area? If not who?

Name: All barriers in place to prevent falling from heights
Tag 1: Are all barriers in place to prevent falling from heights? Has all inserts, blockouts, penetrations, rebates, hobs been securely fixed? If NO, who has been notified?

Name: Adequate access ways to work areas & in deep sections
Tag 1: Is there adequate access ways to work areas and in deep sections of casting elements?

Name: Latest construction drawings checked prior to pour
Tag 1: Latest construction drawings checked prior to pour? Please attach if applicable

Name: Sufficient cover between the reinforcement & formwork
Tag 1: Is there sufficient cover between the reinforcement and formwork for concrete to be placed? If NO, who has been notified?

Name: Enough access in tight areas to sufficiently finish the concrete
Tag 1: Is there enough access in tight areas i.e. near hobs, penetrations for concrete hand-equipment (trowels, etc.) to sufficiently finish the concrete?

Name: Concrete testing booked for this pour element
Tag 1: Has concrete testing been booked for this pour element?

Name: Concrete placed at the correct RL/datum point checked & verified
Tag 1: Has the concrete been placed at the correct RL, datum point checked and verified and in layers as per AS 3600?

Name: Vibration of concrete been undertaken
Tag 1: Has all vibration of concrete been undertaken as per Structural Engineer's requirement and AS 3600?

Name: All curing & concrete protection undertaken
Tag 1: Has all curing and concrete protection been undertaken?

Name: All cleaning in regards to pump hoppers & excess concrete
Tag 1: Has all cleaning in regards to pump hoppers and excess concrete from the pour location been cleared?

Name: An as-built issued
Tag 1: Has an as-built been issued? If no, who is to issue this?

Name: Required floor level finish achieved
Tag 1: Has the required floor level finish been achieved?

Name: All areas checked for non-conformance elements
Tag 1: Has all areas been checked for non-conformance elements?

Name: Attach Post-Pour 3m straight-edge check annotated drawing
Tag 1: Attach Post-Pour 3m straight-edge check annotated drawing (Only applicable for slabs).
